1
00:00:36,180 --> 00:00:40,940
=Ancient Bracelet=

2
00:00:41,340 --> 00:00:44,380
=Episode 21=

3
00:00:44,420 --> 00:00:46,660
=Who Exactly Are You?=

4
00:00:47,390 --> 00:00:48,790
He created an Illusory Realm,

5
00:00:50,320 --> 00:00:51,390
making Wu Zhaoli believe

6
00:00:52,070 --> 00:00:53,350
that you were already dead.

7
00:00:54,110 --> 00:00:55,470
He then lured her

8
00:00:55,470 --> 00:00:57,110
to offer her heart's blood

9
00:00:58,150 --> 00:01:00,320
to mend his wounds
and restore his power.

10
00:01:01,320 --> 00:01:02,280
What did you just say?

11
00:01:04,840 --> 00:01:05,760
Your Majesty,

12
00:01:05,760 --> 00:01:07,430
please, don't go save Wu Zhaoli.

13
00:01:07,680 --> 00:01:09,200
It's too late now.

14
00:01:09,710 --> 00:01:12,000
If Yan Che has drained
her heart's blood,

15
00:01:12,510 --> 00:01:13,680
you won't even stand

16
00:01:14,040 --> 00:01:15,680
a chance against him.

17
00:01:15,950 --> 00:01:17,400
It'd be throwing your life away.

18
00:01:20,950 --> 00:01:21,790
Ye Li,

19
00:01:22,120 --> 00:01:23,790
since you were forced by Yan Che,

20
00:01:23,870 --> 00:01:24,870
I will spare your life.

21
00:01:25,760 --> 00:01:27,680
But if you dare harm Zhaoli again,

22
00:01:28,870 --> 00:01:30,680
I won't hesitate to cripple you myself.

23
00:01:31,120 --> 00:01:31,960
Your Majesty.

24
00:01:32,200 --> 00:01:33,040
Your Majesty.

25
00:01:37,060 --> 00:01:39,220
(Yan Manor)

26
00:01:45,760 --> 00:01:47,230
A cunning hare with many burrows.

27
00:01:59,760 --> 00:02:01,350
He's taken Zhaoli into the illusion.

28
00:02:09,630 --> 00:02:10,960
It's almost done.

29
00:02:16,000 --> 00:02:16,840
Zhaoli.

30
00:02:16,960 --> 00:02:17,820
Zhaoli,

31
00:02:17,870 --> 00:02:18,710
wake up.

32
00:02:21,240 --> 00:02:22,080
Ying Du.

33
00:02:23,520 --> 00:02:24,360
Ying Du.

34
00:02:29,000 --> 00:02:31,000
Am I seeing illusions?

35
00:02:34,750 --> 00:02:35,870
Just a little more.

36
00:02:37,590 --> 00:02:38,430
Ying Du,

37
00:02:39,470 --> 00:02:40,710
before I breathe my last,

38
00:02:42,120 --> 00:02:43,870
I wish to see you one final time.

39
00:02:48,680 --> 00:02:49,560
Zhaoli, stop.

40
00:02:57,800 --> 00:02:58,870
Who is it?

41
00:02:59,543 --> 00:03:00,790
Where's that sound coming from?

42
00:03:01,190 --> 00:03:02,030
Zhaoli,

43
00:03:02,179 --> 00:03:03,746
what you see is all part of an illusion.

44
00:03:03,960 --> 00:03:04,910
None of it is real.

45
00:03:09,800 --> 00:03:10,800
Illusion?

46
00:03:12,840 --> 00:03:13,840
It's not real?

47
00:03:19,630 --> 00:03:22,080
Zhaoli, you're showing signs
of awakening.

48
00:03:25,800 --> 00:03:26,910
Worsen.

49
00:03:29,520 --> 00:03:30,360
Ying Du.

50
00:03:30,840 --> 00:03:32,150
Ying Du, don't scare me like this.

51
00:03:32,870 --> 00:03:34,240
(It's getting more serious.)

52
00:03:34,870 --> 00:03:36,590
(I must speed up the plan.)

53
00:04:02,430 --> 00:04:04,470
How dare you use
Zhaoli's feelings for me

54
00:04:05,240 --> 00:04:06,680
to take her heart's blood?

55
00:04:06,910 --> 00:04:08,310
Stop hiding.

56
00:04:08,400 --> 00:04:09,910
Show me your true face.

57
00:04:15,430 --> 00:04:16,870
Your power is the same as mine.

58
00:04:17,000 --> 00:04:18,560
Fighting like this is pointless.

59
00:04:18,560 --> 00:04:19,600
We should stop.

60
00:04:20,190 --> 00:04:21,070
As for Zhaoli,

61
00:04:21,270 --> 00:04:22,240
you can't save her.

62
00:04:22,503 --> 00:04:24,040
Those trapped inside the Illusion Realm

63
00:04:24,040 --> 00:04:25,510
must awaken on their own.

64
00:04:25,600 --> 00:04:26,600
Any outside interference

65
00:04:26,600 --> 00:04:28,560
will keep her trapped there forever.

66
00:04:28,560 --> 00:04:29,920
Who exactly are you?

67
00:04:30,560 --> 00:04:31,750
Beneath that mask

68
00:04:32,430 --> 00:04:33,720
is your true face, isn't it?

69
00:04:39,160 --> 00:04:40,000
I knew it.

70
00:04:40,510 --> 00:04:41,350
You...

71
00:04:41,830 --> 00:04:42,920
Who are you, really?

72
00:04:48,070 --> 00:04:49,870
I'm bound to you by blood,

73
00:04:50,510 --> 00:04:51,830
your own brother.

74
00:04:54,040 --> 00:04:54,880
You...

75
00:04:55,680 --> 00:04:57,360
We were born together,

76
00:04:57,800 --> 00:04:59,120
sharing the same bloodline.

77
00:04:59,270 --> 00:05:02,430
Why do you get to bask in honor
before others,

78
00:05:02,950 --> 00:05:05,160
while I must change my face,

79
00:05:05,160 --> 00:05:07,560
living as your shadow
with each breath borrowed?

80
00:05:09,160 --> 00:05:10,560
I've never felt joy

81
00:05:11,870 --> 00:05:13,950
for a single moment.

82
00:05:14,720 --> 00:05:16,270
All of this is because of you.

83
00:05:16,920 --> 00:05:18,680
The pain I've endured,

84
00:05:19,270 --> 00:05:20,110
I want you

85
00:05:20,480 --> 00:05:21,950
to pay it back twice over.

86
00:05:22,680 --> 00:05:24,430
So, you took Yan Che's identity

87
00:05:24,870 --> 00:05:27,310
and kept standing
in the way of Zhaoli and me

88
00:05:27,510 --> 00:05:28,600
just to make me suffer.

89
00:05:28,830 --> 00:05:30,120
That's right.

90
00:05:30,390 --> 00:05:32,310
I've borne so much for your sake,

91
00:05:32,800 --> 00:05:34,680
and this is what you owe me.

92
00:05:35,510 --> 00:05:37,190
Do you think this is enough?

93
00:05:37,750 --> 00:05:38,590
I want you to see it,

94
00:05:38,610 --> 00:05:40,720
as the one you love dies before you.

95
00:05:43,720 --> 00:05:44,560
Die!

96
00:05:50,120 --> 00:05:51,920
Ying Du,

97
00:05:51,920 --> 00:05:53,750
I'll never let you die.

98
00:06:01,070 --> 00:06:01,910
(Zhaoli,)

99
00:06:02,240 --> 00:06:04,000
(you'd trade your life for mine.)

100
00:06:19,950 --> 00:06:20,800
Something's wrong.

101
00:06:22,920 --> 00:06:24,480
This is not the real world.

102
00:06:30,000 --> 00:06:32,360
Your body has been drained.

103
00:06:33,680 --> 00:06:36,160
Yet, you still dare
to summon your power.

104
00:06:41,560 --> 00:06:43,120
How can there be two Ying Dus?

105
00:06:56,510 --> 00:06:57,350
Ying Du.

106
00:07:15,510 --> 00:07:16,630
It failed.

107
00:07:16,950 --> 00:07:18,430
From this moment on,

108
00:07:19,070 --> 00:07:21,160
there shall be only one Ying Du
in this world.

109
00:07:23,120 --> 00:07:24,390
And that one is me.

110
00:07:26,750 --> 00:07:28,190
Soul-Swapping Spell.

111
00:07:44,240 --> 00:07:45,080
Ying Du.

112
00:07:45,360 --> 00:07:46,390
Ying Du, don't!

113
00:08:33,120 --> 00:08:34,680
- Zhaoli.
- Ying Du.

114
00:08:35,670 --> 00:08:37,000
Ying Du, are you alright?

115
00:08:40,870 --> 00:08:41,790
That's impossible.

116
00:08:42,270 --> 00:08:44,360
How could you escape
from the Illusion Realm?

117
00:08:49,200 --> 00:08:50,510
The Fengwu Bracelet.

118
00:08:51,200 --> 00:08:52,040
Ying Du,

119
00:08:52,257 --> 00:08:53,956
you actually went this far
to protect her.

120
00:08:54,480 --> 00:08:56,600
You poured all your power
into the Bracelet.

121
00:09:03,550 --> 00:09:04,670
So,

122
00:09:05,270 --> 00:09:07,630
this whole thing was your scheme.

123
00:09:10,990 --> 00:09:15,640
♪Snow falls upon my brows,
blurring suddenly♪

124
00:09:17,470 --> 00:09:22,440
♪Memories turn,
forgiving time after time♪

125
00:09:23,900 --> 00:09:27,180
♪Tears or snowflakes, sweet or bitter♪

126
00:09:27,180 --> 00:09:30,080
♪Hard to tell them apart♪

127
00:09:30,600 --> 00:09:35,890
♪Vowing to give you
three lifetimes' happiness♪

128
00:09:35,890 --> 00:09:39,590
♪In this life, I still run toward you♪

129
00:09:39,940 --> 00:09:42,290
♪No matter the homeward journey♪

130
00:09:42,290 --> 00:09:46,330
♪Falling to the deepest place
in your heart♪

131
00:09:46,330 --> 00:09:48,710
♪And that is enough♪

132
00:09:48,710 --> 00:09:52,500
♪Ahead lies a path without snow or wind♪

133
00:09:52,710 --> 00:09:55,470
♪Begonia blooms across the branches♪

134
00:09:55,840 --> 00:10:01,590
♪One more glance
may let love stand still♪

